By Sampson Unamka Disqualified Erica has disclosed her plans and things she would love to do after her exit from the television reality game show. “Now that I am done with Big Brother, the ventures I will love to go into are obviously my acting, I will love to be a brand ambassador for numerous brands, I will love to go into real estate, I will love to go into beauty businesses also and I will love for my fans to support me.” 